title: Old Sledge - Don't Let Your Deal Go Down (2011)
description:
Old Sledge - Don't Let The Deal Go Down released 2011 Old Sledge was a group from 
the Blue Ridge Mountains of Virginia.
Blowing the dust off old tunes and songs from the golden era of early country, hillbilly and blues music.
This is Redneck Moonshiner music at its best.
